description	"FN-2187 aka 'Finn'

Class: ARC Trooper.
Class Summary: 
A high-mobility jedi/ARC hybrid that can engage enemies at all ranges. 

Weaponry:
- EL-16 (Based on Westar M5 level 2 w/Sniper Attachment)
- Frag Grenades (3)

--- Lightsaber 
- Defense (1)
- Can block lightsabers
- Can block blasters
- Can prevent Pull/Push if holding block

Force powers:
- Sense (2)

Attributes:
- Heal (3)

Abilities:
- Stamina (3) [Class Special 1]
- Dodge (3) [Class Special 1]
- Dexterity (2) [Alt Ability 1]
--- Grappling Hook (2)
- Hold Class Special 2 while melee is equipped, then hold spacebar to ascend or crouch to descend.

After the raid on Jakku, FN-2187 had a profound change of heart, and became a fugitive. He adopts the name 'Finn' instead of his numerical designation. It would seem that Finn's good nature - a gentleness, humour and unerring moral compass - could not be wiped from his mind as it is from others who undergo stormtrooper training."